    <div style="margin: 2rem 0; padding: 1.2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2, #eff6ff); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;"><div style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">📖</div><div style="font-weight: 700; color: #111827; font-size: 1rem;">Learn Chinese Apps Resources</div><div style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.3rem;">Complete Learning Guide</div></div>


  <h2 id="choosing-resources">How to Choose the Right Resources for Your Level</h2>
  <p>With hundreds of Chinese learning apps and websites available, the biggest challenge is not finding resources — it is choosing the <strong>right combination</strong> for your current level. The most successful learners do not use one app; they combine 2–3 tools that cover different skills.</p>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
    <div style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🌱</div>
      <strong>Beginner (HSK 1–2)</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Focus on: pronunciation, basic vocabulary, character recognition, simple sentences</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #eff6ff; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">📘</div>
      <strong>Intermediate (HSK 3–4)</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Focus on: grammar patterns, reading practice, listening comprehension, conversation</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fdf2f8; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🎯</div>
      <strong>Advanced (HSK 5–6)</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Focus on: native content, nuance, idioms, writing, academic/business Chinese</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
    <strong>🔑 Golden Rule:</strong> Every study session should include at least two of the four skills — <strong>reading, listening, speaking, writing</strong>. An app that only covers vocabulary is not enough on its own.
  </div>

