        <li><strong>Decipher Chinese</strong> — news summaries with vocabulary aids</li>
        <li><strong>Chinese children's books</strong> — simple language with pictures</li>
        <li><strong>Weibo / 小红书</strong> — real social media posts (short, colloquial)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fdf2f8; border: 2px solid #ec4899; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
      <strong style="color: #db2777;">🎯 Advanced Reading</strong>
      <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
