        <li><strong>知乎 (Zhihu)</strong> — Chinese Q&A platform (like Quora)</li>
        <li><strong>微信公众号</strong> — WeChat public accounts on topics you enjoy</li>
        <li><strong>News apps</strong> — 今日头条, BBC Chinese, 南华早报</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="speaking-practice">Speaking and Pronunciation Practice</h2>
  <p>Speaking is the hardest skill to practice alone, but it is not impossible. Here are practical ways to improve your spoken Chinese without a personal tutor:</p>

  <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
    <thead>
