        <td style="padding: 10px;">Play native audio and speak along simultaneously</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">10 min/day</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #ffffff;">
        <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>Record & Compare</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Record yourself, then compare to a native speaker</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">5 min/day</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #f8fafc;">
        <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>Language Exchange</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Tandem or HelloTalk — practice with native speakers</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">30 min/session</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #ffffff;">
        <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>Self-Narration</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Describe what you are doing in Chinese as you do it</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Anytime</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #f8fafc;">
        <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>AI Conversation</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Use AI chatbots with voice for speaking practice</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">15 min/session</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #ffffff;">
        <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>Tone Pair Drills</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Practice all 20 tone combinations systematically</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">5 min/day</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>Use our <a href="/chinese/tools/pinyin-converter/">Pinyin Converter</a> to check the correct pinyin and tones for any text you are practicing, and review our <a href="/chinese/blog/chinese-tones-guide/">Complete Tones Guide</a> for detailed tone training methods.</p>

